The '''Northwest Atlantic Fisheries Centre''' is a [[Government of Canada]] research facility and office complex located in [[St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador|St. John's]], [[Newfoundland and Labrador]].
It is primarily used by the [[Department of Fisheries and Oceans]].
